Welcome to the OSS Pioneer series of interviews featuring China's IT thought-leaders on all things Open Source. 
For the next interview, let's meet Alan Ren, General Manager of VMware China R&D Center and the co-founder of “VMware Innovation Network“. He is responsible for the innovations of advanced technologies including Cloud Computing, Internet of Things, Artificial Intelligence and Blockchain with the concept of “Diversity, Symbiosis, and Tech for Good".
